Template: baize-kube/consumers
Type: string
Default:
Description: Kubernetes cluster consumers
 Which users should have access to the Kubernetes cluster?
 .
 Enter usernames separated by spaces. These users will be added
 to the 'baize-consumers' group and will be able to access the
 cluster once provisioned.
 .
 For unattended installs, create /etc/baize-kube/consumers.conf
 with one username per line before running dpkg -i.
